snippet.title: Caravan Chaos Trailer
snippet.description:
In Caravan Chaos you wreck your friends by launching your caravan at them. 
Up to four players duke it out in a destroyable arena, the last van standing wins!
Local and online multiplayer fun across four different game modes. 

https://www.instagram.com/caravan_chaos/
https://twitter.com/CaravanChaos
https://www.facebook.com/Caravan-Chaos-110805223670302/

Developed by Daniel Wiendl, Michael Schwaiger, Gabriel Koidl and Michael Etschbacher from the FH Salzburg.
Logo Art by Johanna Lehmert.

This game was funded with the help of AWS.
